general.gigTitle: create shopify dropshipping store and custom shopify website development

sellerCard.description:
Hello,
I'm Abbas Ahmad (Zamarr), a software engineer with six years of web development experience. I specialize in designing themes and landing pages, enhancing user experiences, and fixing errors in existing online stores. Additionally, I can convert designs from PSD, AI, Figma, and Sketch into responsive Shopify pages. I create customized email templates for platforms like Mailchimp and Klaviyo. My expertise extends to optimizing product pages for better sales performance and providing valuable tips to enhance e-commerce businesses. Feel free to inbox me!

description.content:
In this gig, I offer complete services of Shopify platform. With over six years of experience collaborating with Shopify, I became a trusted Fiverr Seller and Shopify partner.


I have successfully delivered more than 300 Shopify Stores with a neat record of all positive reviews.


What you will get?

  • Responsive Shopify website with Modern Looking design for all screens
  • Custom theme designing to match your brand
  • Modern Landing pages (up to 15)
  • Product page optimization
  • Apps and plugin integration
  • Autoresponders (Shopify Email Notifications)
  • Live Chat (Shopify Inbox)
  • Shopify Markets
  • Coupon Setup (Discount Codes)
  • Product reviews
  • Payment gateway setup
  • Fast loading and optimized Shopify store
  • Accessibility to prevent law suits
  • Email Marketting through Klaviyo | Mailchimp


Why Choose Me?

  • Proven experience for creating professional Shopify Stores
  • Personalized and custom Shopify website design
  • Fluent English speaker


Premium Support:

  • Lifetime premium support for all Packages


Graphic designing work not included.


Let's create a stunning Shopify Store | Shopify website that exceeds your expectations!


Do inbox before placing your order so we can discuss all the details.


Best Regards!

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide all services related to shopify?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I provide all the services related to Shopify platform, and this gig is a one-stop solution for all your Shopify needs.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What do you need to get started?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I assume, you create your Shopify account so just need the URL of your store, which will look like "yourstore.myshopify.com", after I will send the collaborator request to your registered email, You can send all the requirements in inbox. and i can create a store for you.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you customize my existing store?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I will customize your existing Shopify store following your requirements.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you convert my psd, figma, sketch, XD designs to Shopify?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes I will, Please inbox your designs in png or jpg. so I can estimate the work and time required for it.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Can you work in a Store built in other than English language?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I can work in almost every language, Like Hebrew, Arabic, German, all.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide any support after the order is completed?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I will provide maintenance support for 7 days, and lifetime support for the bugs in my code.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Is all of the above prices is fixed?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: No, not at all. Please inbox your requirements  I will review and quote accordingly.
